Name: familial hypobetalipoproteinemia 2
Definition: A hypobetalipoproteinemia that has material_basis_in homozygous or compound heterozygous mutation in the ANGPTL3 gene on chromosome 1p31.

Name: familial hypobetalipoproteinemia 1
Definition: A hypobetalipoproteinemia that has material_basis_in mutation in the APOB gene on chromosome 2p24.
